  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill Ze Bugs is a time survival shooter with minimalistic gameplay and roguelike elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 2137 AD, humanity's last source of protein were massive, genetically engineered insects. However, they escaped their vats, and now the humanity became the primary source of protein for the giant BUGS.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill ze bugs and survive, or fail and get consumed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335070/extras/8cc5a37fe63c14692c0e2dbcf9d9bc53.avif?t=1737625239\" width=427 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >minimalistic \"bullet heaven\" gameplay with roguelike elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ unique augments, ranging from a simple stat upgrade to run-altering transformations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 playable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >secret synergies to discover</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >several enemy types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >metaprogression</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill Ze Bugs is a time survival shooter with minimalistic gameplay and roguelike elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 2137 AD, humanity's last source of protein were massive, genetically engineered insects. However, they escaped their vats, and now the humanity became the primary source of protein for the giant BUGS.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill ze bugs and survive, or fail and get consumed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335070/extras/8cc5a37fe63c14692c0e2dbcf9d9bc53.avif?t=1737625239\" width=427 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >minimalistic \"bullet heaven\" gameplay with roguelike elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ unique augments, ranging from a simple stat upgrade to run-altering transformations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 playable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >secret synergies to discover</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >several enemy types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >metaprogression</p></li></ul>",
